exceptions.tactic: rewrite (pluspf_com A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs eqA_dec n ltM ltM_dec p (mults a p)).
exceptions.exn: In environment A : Set A0, A1 : A eqA : A -> A -> Prop plusA : A -> A -> A invA : A -> A minusA, multA : A -> A -> A divA : A -> forall b : A, ~ eqA b A0 -> A cs : CoefStructure A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA eqA_dec : forall a b : A, {eqA a b} + {~ eqA a b} n : nat ltM : mon n -> mon n -> Prop ltM_dec : forall a b : mon n, {ltM a b} + {ltM b a} + {a = b} os : OrderStructure (mon n) (zero_mon n) ltM (mult_mon n) p : list (Term A n) a : Term A n H : eqP A eqA n p (pO A n) The term "p" has type "list (Term A n)" while it is expected to have type "OrderStructure (mon n) (zero_mon n) ltM (mult_mon n)".

original: simpl. intros. rewrite (pluspf_com A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs eqA_dec n ltM ltM_dec p (mults a p)). reflexivity.
